  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流追踪系统的数据流图。核心场景是：外部系统通过运单号查询配送路线，这个流程涉及车队管理和数据源过滤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以起点是APIClient，它携带的是运单号信息？然后需要找哪个组件来处理这个请求？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，APIClient代表外部调用方，它把过滤条件发给DeviceController。DeviceController对应我们的配送路线服务，负责协调整个查询流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把APIClient指向DeviceController，标注为\"sends filter input\"。然后DeviceController需要用到车队管理的过滤配置对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，DeviceController会使用DeviceFilterInput来获取车队管理的过滤规则。但注意DeviceFilterInput和后面的数据获取组件都是复用车队管理这个逻辑模块的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我注意到DeviceController既要\"uses\" DeviceFilterInput，又要委派给另一个组件去真正拉数据。是不是应该有个DeviceDataFetcher专门负责数据获取？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceDataFetcher"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，DeviceController把实际的数据获取任务delegate给DeviceDataFetcher。DeviceDataFetcher再去应用过滤条件查询数据源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "delegates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "DeviceDataFetcher指向DataSource，标注\"applies filters\"。DataSource也是基于运单号的对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，DataSource代表运单号对应的数据存储。DeviceDataFetcher查完之后要把结果返回给DeviceController，最后DeviceController再响应给APIClient。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上返回链路：DeviceDataFetcher到DeviceController是\"returns results\"，DeviceController到APIClient是\"responds\"。这样流程就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DeviceController",
        "APIClient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说的有点问题。DeviceFilterInput和DeviceDataFetcher虽然都涉及车队管理，但它们是不同的节点，一个是配置输入，一个是执行组件，不能合并。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，保持两个独立节点，都标注为Logistics_FleetManagement模块。整个流程是：APIClient发过滤条件→DeviceController用配置、委派Fetcher→Fetcher过滤查数据源→结果返回→响应客户端。确认这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APIClient",
        "DeviceController",
        "DeviceFilterInput",
        "DeviceDataFetcher",
        "DataSource"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确，这就是我们要的物流追踪数据流。",
